{"TopicId":174601,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"Shower thoughts","CreatedByName":"p1t1o","CreatedById":74091,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-04T14:42:24Z","PageNum":6,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Fraston","CreatedById":188565,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-05T15:09:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOooh yeah\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-05T16:20:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223393425\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174601\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221528210444\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002274091\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022p1t1o\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, p1t1o said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf the Illumanati were still around...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow many illuminati does it take to illuminate a room?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"razark","CreatedById":32993,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-05T17:06:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223393474\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174601\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221528215627\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n45 minutes ago, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow many illuminati does it take to illuminate a room?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey wouldn\u0027t, because they like to keep people in the dark.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-05T17:47:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSince the sun is about 44% as bright on Mars as it is here, you might not need to wear sun shades when walking there.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bill Phil","CreatedById":127797,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-05T20:27:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223393537\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174601\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221528220869\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150330\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022cubinator\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, cubinator said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSince the sun is about 44% as bright on Mars as it is here, you might not need to wear sun shades when walking there.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDepends on how reflective the surface is.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kernel Kraken","CreatedById":181383,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-06T00:26:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223374635\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174601\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221525876155\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289014\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022adsii1970\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 5/9/2018 at 9:29 AM, adsii1970 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, there is. If you don\u0027t want poop all over the place...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut the point is, you\u0027re constantly having to take the dog out... and in some cases, the dog gets separation anxiety. And that can be real fun...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStep 1: open door, dog runs outside\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStep 2: dog drops a deuce in backyard\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStep 3: dog runs back in\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStep 4: said deuce composts into fertilizer for the lawn after a few months or so. We have the greenest backyard in the neighborhood!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-06-06T00:26:37Z\u0022 title=\u002206/06/2018 12:26  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EJune 6, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Kernel Kraken\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-06T04:36:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223393537\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174601\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221528220869\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150330\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022cubinator\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, cubinator said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSince the sun is about 44% as bright on Mars as it is here, you might not need to wear sun shades when walking there.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut since Mars doesn\u0027t have a thick atmosphere and ozone layer, UV should be more intense.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"p1t1o","CreatedById":74091,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-06T08:30:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223393811\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174601\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221528244761\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022181383\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kernel Kraken\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 hours ago, Kernel Kraken said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStep 1: open door, dog runs outside\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStep 2: dog drops a deuce in backyard\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStep 3: dog runs back in\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStep 4: said deuce composts into fertilizer for the lawn after a few months or so. We have the greenest backyard in the neighborhood!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDude. No.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-07T16:51:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf a gum neutralizes the sour\u00A0 in the mouth, why shouldn\u0027t it keep doing this in the stomach, when you are chewing it after lunch and swallowing the saliva?\u003Cbr\u003E\nShouldn\u0027t it disturb the digestion? Or it\u0027s a choice: either teeth, or stomach?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheTripleAce3","CreatedById":188116,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-07T21:02:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223393934\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174601\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221528259782\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 6/6/2018 at 12:36 AM, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut since Mars doesn\u0027t have a thick atmosphere and ozone layer, UV should be more intense.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1.14 diff in apparent magnitude tho?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-08T03:21:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223395089\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174601\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221528405363\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022188116\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022TheTripleAce3\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, TheTripleAce3 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1.14 diff in apparent magnitude tho?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo, sunglasses are still in fashion.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NSEP","CreatedById":165635,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-08T06:17:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEveryone who goes skydiving will die.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-08T06:24:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nChess, too.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NSEP","CreatedById":165635,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-08T15:08:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf something happends 1 lightyear away and im seeing it right now, does that mean it happend 1 year ago, because the light had to travel 1 year, or is it right now, because if\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Enothing\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0moves faster than light, then than must mean time itself also doesn\u0027t move faster than light.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhoa.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Atlas2342","CreatedById":155194,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-08T15:28:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223395528\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174601\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221528470506\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022165635\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022NSEP\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n18 minutes ago, NSEP said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf something happends 1 lightyear away and im seeing it right now, does that mean it happend 1 year ago, because the light had to travel 1 year, or is it right now, because if\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Enothing\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0moves faster than light, then than must mean time itself also doesn\u0027t move faster than light.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhoa.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThen, it happened one year ago, didn\u2019t it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NSEP","CreatedById":165635,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-08T15:31:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223395539\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174601\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221528471703\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022155194\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Atlas2342\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, Atlas2342 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThen, it happened one year ago, didn\u2019t it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWait, time travels at the exact same speed time does? Oh wait, yes! Of course!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Atlas2342","CreatedById":155194,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-08T15:37:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223395544\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174601\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221528471910\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022165635\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022NSEP\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, NSEP said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWait, time travels at the exact same speed time does? Oh wait, yes! Of course!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAn explosion happens far away from you. The shockwave takes 60 minutes to get to you. When the shockwave reaches you, the explosion would have happened an hour ago. Same principle.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso related, people who were born at the same time can be born a day apart.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NSEP","CreatedById":165635,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-08T15:41:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223395545\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174601\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221528472234\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022155194\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Atlas2342\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Atlas2342 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso related, people who were born at the same time can be born a day apart.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, because light has to travel a da.... here we go again.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u002214608107_1180665285312703_1558693314_n.j\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022450\u0022 src=\u0022http://i0.kym-cdn.com/entries/icons/mobile/000/021/464/14608107_1180665285312703_1558693314_n.jpg\u0022 width=\u0022800\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-08T18:32:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223395528\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174601\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221528470506\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022165635\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022NSEP\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, NSEP said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf something happends 1 lightyear away and im seeing it right now, does that mean it happend 1 year ago, because the light had to travel 1 year, or is it right now, because if\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Enothing\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0moves faster than light, then than must mean time itself also doesn\u0027t move faster than light.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo, Big Bang is happening right now. We can see it all around.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NSEP","CreatedById":165635,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-08T19:10:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOn to another shower thought:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLets say i go on a cruise ship with 4000 other people, jokingly tell my friends that the ship is going to sink, and later, the ship actually sinks. Is that a coincidence, or inevitable, because you would think that at least a few of the 4001\u00A0people on board would make a joke about the ship sinking?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-08T19:58:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223395674\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174601\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221528485057\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022165635\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022NSEP\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n45 minutes ago, NSEP said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOn to another shower thought:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLets say i go on a cruise ship with 4000 other people, jokingly tell my friends that the ship is going to sink, and later, the ship actually sinks. Is that a coincidence, or inevitable, because you would think that at least a few of the 4001\u00A0people on board would make a joke about the ship sinking?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s probably likely that a few people would joke about the ship sinking on any cruise ship, so you could happen to be on the one that actually does by a slim chance.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-09T02:03:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen people go to Mars, we should have scheduled \u0027waving times\u0027 set up by internet so that for a short time, people on Earth can wave at Mars and the astronauts can be waving back at the same time (this would be some compromise between Earth and Mars time involving either one group waving early, or the two groups waving in a bounce). Of course, nobody would be able to see the other group waving, but it would be fun to know there is somebody waving back.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-09T05:42:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223395674\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174601\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221528485057\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022165635\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022NSEP\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, NSEP said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLets say i go on a cruise ship with 4000 other people, jokingly tell my friends that the ship is going to sink, and later, the ship actually sinks. Is that a coincidence, or inevitable, because you would think that at least a few of the 4001\u00A0people on board would make a joke about the ship sinking?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe ship sank because somebody \u003Cem\u003Enot\u003C/em\u003E joking about sinking has an evil eye.\u003Cbr\u003E\nHe/she was thinking: \u0022We are not sinking. It\u0027s OK. What can go wrong?\u0022, and that\u0027s a result.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223395875\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174601\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221528509813\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150330\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022cubinator\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, cubinator said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen people go to Mars, we should have scheduled \u0027waving times\u0027 set up by internet so that for a short time, people on Earth can wave at Mars and the astronauts can be waving back at the same time (this would be some compromise between Earth and Mars time involving either one group waving early, or the two groups waving in a bounce). Of course, nobody would be able to see the other group waving, but it would be fun to know there is somebody waving back.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd we will easily recognize that moments from internet freezing, when all Martian users will be connecting at once.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-06-09T05:50:47Z\u0022 title=\u002206/09/2018 05:50  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EJune 9, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by kerbiloid\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-09T16:39:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223395947\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174601\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221528522926\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd we will easily recognize that moments from internet freezing, when all Martian users will be connecting at once.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou wouldn\u0027t have to connect all at once. You\u0027d set up a time in advance, then when the time comes everybody goes outside and literally waves at the other planet.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-09T16:46:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223396272\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174601\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221528562354\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150330\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022cubinator\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 minutes ago, cubinator said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou wouldn\u0027t have to connect all at once. You\u0027d set up a time in advance, then when the time comes everybody goes outside and literally waves at the other planet.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd myriads of Martian leechers resume torrent downloading\u00A0at once.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-06-09T16:47:11Z\u0022 title=\u002206/09/2018 04:47  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EJune 9, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by kerbiloid\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}